    <item>
      <title>泰国政局动荡 保皇派仍牢牢掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国领导人上任不到一年就被赶下台，这清楚地表明了一件事：过去二十年来，在军方支持下长期实行统治的保皇派政权仍然掌握着全部权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析发现美国国内骚乱威胁较低但正在上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/threat-of-us-civil-unrest-is-low-but-rising-analysis-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博经济研究试图捕捉特朗普遇刺事件后美国国民不安情绪的分析显示，在明年全球最有可能陷入暴力政治动荡的经济体中，美国仅次于土耳其和俄罗斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/threat-of-us-civil-unrest-is-low-but-rising-analysis-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 15:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与伊朗紧张局势升温 加沙停火谈判重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/gaza-cease-fire-talks-to-resume-as-israel-iran-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙停火谈判的国际调解人定于周四与以色列谈判人员会面，这是达成协议的最新尝试，他们希望此举能避免中东地区暴力事件可能升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/gaza-cease-fire-talks-to-resume-as-israel-iran-tensions-simmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 15:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业警告英国要保护工人权利改革的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/business-warns-uk-to-protect-growth-in-workers-rights-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自上个月大选以来，英国商界领袖在与部长和工会首次会谈中敦促基尔·斯塔默领导的英国政府确保其加强工人权利的计划不会抑制经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/business-warns-uk-to-protect-growth-in-workers-rights-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 15:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典呼吁北欧国家共同努力阻止枪支犯罪蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sweden-calls-for-nordic-effort-to-stop-gun-crime-from-spreading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典司法部长 Gunnar Strommer 在丹麦发生一系列瑞典人暴力犯罪事件后表示，瑞典将与北欧地区的政府和当局合作，防止帮派暴力蔓延到境外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sweden-calls-for-nordic-effort-to-stop-gun-crime-from-spreading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国怀疑俄罗斯参与破坏军事基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-suspects-russian-hand-in-sabotage-at-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柏林一位资深议员称，德国正在调查俄罗斯可能对两个军事基地实施的破坏行为，据称有人试图污染饮用水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/germany-suspects-russian-hand-in-sabotage-at-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦考虑征收商品出口税以缩小预算缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kazakhstan-may-tax-metals-commodities-exports-seeking-more-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，哈萨克斯坦今年正考虑对金属和燃料等原材料出口征税，以帮助弥补预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kazakhstan-may-tax-metals-commodities-exports-seeking-more-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院裁定总理在道德案件中罪名成立，将其免职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院裁定总理斯雷塔·塔维辛违反道德规范，解除其职务，这导致这个东南亚国家陷入新一轮的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚发展债券在信心测试中吸引强劲需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kenya-s-development-bond-sale-will-be-key-market-confidence-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在反政府抗议浪潮导致当局放弃一项关键的增税计划之后，肯尼亚发售的基础设施债券吸引了强劲需求，这是对投资者兴趣的一次重要考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kenya-s-development-bond-sale-will-be-key-market-confidence-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
